Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.39,0:08:35.26,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,友加里 早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.62,0:08:40.01,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,你從剛剛開始都在幹嘛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.07,0:08:42.50,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.70,0:08:43.66,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,一起走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.46,0:08:45.86,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.09,0:08:50.34,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我好像看到早苗在前面
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.36,0:08:51.79,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,友加里有看到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.32,0:08:53.96,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,不  我沒看到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.97,0:09:00.43,Takagi san—Picture 02-2,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1484,324)}{\fad(450,450)}隨身物品檢查
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.16,0:09:06.73,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,說起來 今天好像要檢查隨身物品
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.40,0:09:09.11,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.90,0:09:11.91,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,咦  你一點都不慌嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.48,0:09:14.25,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我又沒有帶什麼不能帶的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.74,0:09:15.68,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,你確定？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.22,0:09:20.42,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,你這麼一問  我還真不敢確定了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.88,0:09:24.42,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,萬一我一不留神把漫畫或者遊戲帶來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.74,0:09:29.24,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,都怪高木同學  我越來越慌了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.34,0:09:34.78,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,那我們就預演一下隨身物品檢查吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.12,0:09:36.53,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,這有什麼意義嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.06,0:09:39.84,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,現在確認一遍  真要檢查的時候不就放心了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.08,0:09:44.24,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,那麼開始檢查
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.26,0:09:53.66,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,不由得緊張起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.42,0:09:56.34,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,沒有問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.64,0:09:58.52,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,西片同學
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.44,0:10:01.36,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,對老師要用敬語
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.48,0:10:03.36,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,完全進入老師的角色了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.54,0:10:04.94,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.37,0:10:05.90,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.37,0:10:10.88,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,啊  這是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.36,0:10:13.15,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,怎麼了  發生什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.38,0:10:14.73,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我帶了什麼不該帶的東西嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.81,0:10:19.42,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我以為是什麼  原來只是教科書
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.93,0:10:20.33,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.11,0:10:21.82,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,嚇了一跳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.60,0:10:25.76,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,沒有被嚇到
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.42,0:10:31.24,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我才沒有被您嚇到
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.42,0:10:33.18,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.60,0:10:36.28,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,那這回輪到我了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.07,0:10:38.35,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.48,0:10:43.05,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,請多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.63,0:10:44.01,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.39,0:10:47.20,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,讓我嚇一嚇高木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.62,0:10:53.68,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,嗯什麼的  西片心目中的大人形象挺有趣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.08,0:10:54.48,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.04,0:10:57.38,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,要對老師使用敬語
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.94,0:10:58.70,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.18,0:11:02.65,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,高木同學這傢伙  現在老師可是我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.48,0:11:10.43,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,一副從容的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.00,0:11:13.90,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,看來她什麼違禁物品都沒帶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.00,0:11:16.56,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,那我只能虛張聲勢一下了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.18,0:11:21.31,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,運動服好像鼓鼓的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.26,0:11:26.56,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,難道說  她從容的表情是裝的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.05,0:11:28.10,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,老師怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.74,0:11:30.56,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,試著套一下她的話吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.62,0:11:34.40,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,你的運動服裡是不是藏了東西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.87,0:11:35.95,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,您可以檢查一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.48,0:11:39.08,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,來  您請您請
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.56,0:11:47.88,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,咦  怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.22,0:11:51.07,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,太羞恥了  我怎麼可能碰她的運動服
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.66,0:11:52.05,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,5…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.14,0:11:54.93,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,4…3…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.99,0:11:56.14,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,等…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.14,0:11:56.52,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,2…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.72,0:11:58.22,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,1…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.50,0:12:01.61,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,0 時間到
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.01,0:12:03.86,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,為什麼定規則的是高木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.09,0:12:06.00,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,明明我才是老師
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.23,0:12:07.49,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,真可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.54,0:12:09.84,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,不過今天不用檢查隨身物品呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.03,0:12:10.40,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.94,0:12:12.42,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我只是覺得可能會有
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.76,0:12:16.72,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,只是在捉弄我而已嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.54,0:12:18.35,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.44,0:12:23.16,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,給  謝謝你借我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.62,0:12:24.53,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我就知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.28,0:12:28.80,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,西片老師太天真了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.30,0:12:37.90,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,你可以隨時檢查我的隨身物品哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.01,0:12:40.54,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,可惡的高木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.86,0:12:44.36,Takagi san—Picture 02-3,,0,0,0,,{\pos(448,406)}圖書委員
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.42,0:12:46.37,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,那麼…文化祭委員就
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.78,0:12:48.28,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,木村和月本來當
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.87,0:12:50.18,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,圖書委員…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.68,0:12:53.02,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,書的背面裝有借書卡對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.58,0:12:57.23,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,拿出卡片讓學生填上名字和日期
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.52,0:12:59.43,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,然後收好卡片
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.87,0:13:02.40,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,書還回來了就寫上歸還日期
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.41,0:13:03.41,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,再將卡片放回書中
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.24,0:13:06.06,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,大概就是這樣  很簡單吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.94,0:13:09.76,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,就這樣  雖然應該沒多少人來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.80,0:13:11.04,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,但要認真幹哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.02,0:13:18.17,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,以後咱每週都有一天不能午休了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.68,0:13:19.41,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,沒什麼不好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.98,0:13:21.72,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,看看書的話很快就結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.88,0:13:24.01,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,書啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.26,0:13:25.79,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,讀起來很有趣的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.16,0:13:27.96,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,高木同學經常讀書嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.38,0:13:30.42,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,跟看漫畫五五開吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.10,0:13:32.95,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,西片看起來不太讀書呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.82,0:13:36.58,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我也讀的啊  時不時的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.79,0:13:40.85,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,反正挺閒的  我去拿點書來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.20,0:13:48.28,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,書麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.37,0:13:55.77,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,提不起什麼興趣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.80,0:13:58.84,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,有沒有什麼想看的…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.88,0:14:05.61,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,恐龍
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.64,0:14:08.49,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,圖鑑真棒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.15,0:14:10.50,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,找到什麼好書了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.58,0:14:13.00,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,不  沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.12,0:14:14.97,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,好險
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.31,0:14:17.52,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,她絕對會覺得我看圖鑑很幼稚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.79,0:14:20.59,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我說  我想了一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.90,0:14:23.68,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,要不要交換兩人找到的書來看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.04,0:14:25.88,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,誒？可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.32,0:14:26.96,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,那就定了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.85,0:14:43.61,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我沒看過這本書呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.98,0:14:44.78,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,講什麼的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.26,0:14:48.04,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我也不清楚  隨便選的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.51,0:14:52.81,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,恐龍圖鑑？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.56,0:14:56.10,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,看你饒有興致地在讀這本書
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.58,0:14:58.66,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,還是被發現了
