Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.26,0:15:15.29,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,高木同學看書的樣子真適合她
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.20,0:15:19.19,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,你在看我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.98,0:15:21.54,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,不  我沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.96,0:15:24.61,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,哦  我懂了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.12,0:15:26.84,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,難得有機會兩人獨處
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.36,0:15:29.99,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,你在伺機把平日被我捉弄的份報復回來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.29,0:15:36.37,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,差不多是這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.10,0:15:39.71,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.14,0:15:42.38,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.50,0:15:46.10,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,誒  那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.15,0:15:47.80,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,「聽八乙女如是說道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.04,0:15:49.63,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,田中的果汁掉落在地
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.12,0:15:52.28,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,操場響徹著棒球部成員們的嘶喊…」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.24,0:15:52.29,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,在朗誦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.84,0:15:55.60,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,怎麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.47,0:15:58.80,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,可惡的高木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.60,0:16:04.81,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,結果一個人都沒來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.10,0:16:06.96,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,下週也這樣就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.30,0:16:09.99,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.49,0:16:14.16,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,下週西片也讀點什麼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.04,0:16:18.05,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,有什麼推薦的書嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.24,0:16:21.43,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我想想
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.10,0:16:24.36,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,除了今天西片給我的書
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.52,0:16:25.64,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,全部都可以推薦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.86,0:16:28.07,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,什麼  那本書有那麼糟糕？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.47,0:16:30.34,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,沒有  很有意思哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.07,0:16:32.90,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,只是不推薦西片讀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.47,0:16:34.41,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,幾個意思
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.70,0:16:38.09,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,因為會暴露書裡沒有那句話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.28,0:16:40.55,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,誒  什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.78,0:16:42.15,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.19,0:16:44.31,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,不對吧  你剛才說了什麼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.16,0:16:46.44,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,高木同學？啥情況？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.86,0:16:50.36,Takagi san—Picture 02-5,,0,0,0,,{\frz269.7\pos(150,362)}夕陽
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.19,0:16:56.24,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,西片
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.08,0:17:00.05,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,高木同學  你在幹嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.34,0:17:01.20,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,跑腿
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.39,0:17:02.21,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,西片你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.72,0:17:03.75,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我在跑步
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.16,0:17:04.83,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.61,0:17:06.58,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,你經常跑嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.80,0:17:08.95,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,也就偶爾跑啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.22,0:17:11.83,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,之前為了備戰馬拉松大賽而跑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.94,0:17:13.44,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,結果還上癮了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.35,0:17:15.78,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,你還練過這個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.54,0:17:17.83,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,雖然輸給我了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.97,0:17:18.18,Takagi san—Picture 02-6,,0,0,0,,{\frz4.675\fad(300,450)\move(1024,344,1024,358,0,1650)}女生折返
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.27,0:17:20.38,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,完蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.30,0:17:22.53,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,下次我會贏你的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.60,0:17:24.47,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我很期待哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.12,0:17:26.74,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,那你要跑多遠呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.58,0:17:30.15,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,還挺看心情的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.46,0:17:32.18,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,跑累了就回去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.47,0:17:34.45,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,上次都跑到那頭的海邊了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.68,0:17:35.51,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,那頭？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.68,0:17:40.66,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,高木同學難得在佩服我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.12,0:17:42.25,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,這下我得…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.54,0:17:43.27,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.48,0:17:44.63,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,當然是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.02,0:17:47.13,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,那還相當遠呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.54,0:17:48.84,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,你說的是真話吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.86,0:17:50.90,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,絕對是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.06,0:17:55.06,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,算了  那你加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.12,0:17:57.09,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.76,0:17:59.55,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,她肯定沒相信
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.06,0:18:02.61,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,行  現在我就跑到海邊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.70,0:18:04.50,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,拍照為證發給她
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.54,0:18:07.51,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,可惡的高木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.94,0:18:10.02,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我要讓你承認我的厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.78,0:18:14.75,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,好難受
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.69,0:18:29.20,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,本來遇到高木同學時就打算回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.48,0:18:30.77,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,體力不夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.98,0:18:36.09,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,好難受
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.60,0:18:38.65,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,要放棄嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.85,0:18:43.64,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,不  我要努力
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.28,0:18:45.40,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,只要到了海邊…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.30,0:18:47.85,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,哇  西片好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.08,0:18:49.33,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我再也不會捉弄你了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.44,0:18:50.56,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,她就會這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.64,0:18:58.10,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,等著瞧吧  高木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.88,0:19:04.83,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,到了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.30,0:19:18.12,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,滿滿的成就感
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.00,0:19:20.73,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,不對  不是想這個的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.89,0:19:22.65,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,得趕緊給高木同學發照片
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.43,0:19:25.39,Takagi san—Picture 02-7,,0,0,0,,{\frz12.75\move(860,136,874,188,0,1943)}{\fs40\t(0,2000,\fs35)}高木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.43,0:19:24.64,Takagi san—Picture 02-8,,0,0,0,,{\frz12.75\move(1024,250,1026,280,0,1150)}{\fs40\t(0,2000,\fs35)}為什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.43,0:19:24.60,Takagi san—Picture 02-8,,0,0,0,,{\frz12.75\move(1110,586,1102,582,24,1150)}{\fs40\t(0,2000,\fs35)}我到海邊了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.60,0:19:25.39,Takagi san—Picture 02-8,,0,0,0,,{\frz12.75\move(1090,522,1024,304,0,250,)}我到海邊了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.47,0:19:25.46,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,選中發送
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.96,0:19:27.68,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,可惡的高木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.90,0:19:29.36,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,好好領教我的厲害吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.23,0:19:32.69,Takagi san—Picture 02-8,,0,0,0,,{\an1\frz12.55\move(740,420,736,478,0,750)}夕陽好美啊。謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.91,0:19:39.54,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,重點不是那個啊  是海啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.68,0:19:40.26,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,這下不就變成
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.40,0:19:43.12,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我只是在分享夕陽給高木同學看而已嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.26,0:19:43.99,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,難道不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.88,0:19:51.94,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,高木同學  你怎麼在這
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.91,0:19:55.63,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,真是不錯的反應
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.39,0:19:59.84,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,跑完腿後騎車飛奔過來也值了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.76,0:20:01.01,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,給你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.47,0:20:07.41,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,謝謝…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.73,0:20:20.88,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我猜你會不會為了給我看證據
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.90,0:20:23.04,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,就一路跑到海邊來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.71,0:20:24.96,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,果然如此
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.42,0:20:28.42,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我又被耍了個團團轉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.94,0:20:31.25,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,不過我很高興
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.79,0:20:34.65,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,因為西片為了給我發夕陽的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.87,0:20:37.23,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,努力跑過來了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.30,0:20:40.60,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,是這樣  但又不是這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.98,0:20:42.77,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,紅通通的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.08,0:20:45.71,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,沒有…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.76,0:20:46.32,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,夕陽
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.38,0:20:50.32,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.03,0:20:53.16,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,不過西片的臉更紅
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.19,0:20:57.45,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,可惡  我只是想讓她覺得我了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.60,0:20:59.67,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,僅僅是在為這個努力的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.24,0:21:03.93,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,追在西片身後真是值了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.63,0:21:09.72,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,能和西片一起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.65,0:21:11.38,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,看夕陽呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.58,0:21:16.73,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,好漂亮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.12,0:21:26.47,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,不不  她在說謊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.81,0:21:28.17,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,她來只是為了捉弄我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.30,0:21:29.35,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,可不能被騙了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.42,0:21:31.17,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,該死
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.40,0:21:34.37,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,還有一絲心動的我真是太蠢了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.67,0:21:38.44,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,不過話說回來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.92,0:21:40.01,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,西片真厲害呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.68,0:21:42.47,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,竟然真的能跑到海邊來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.86,0:21:55.49,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,也沒什麼啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.77,0:21:58.90,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,西片  被我誇了在偷笑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.17,0:22:00.36,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我可沒偷笑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.73,0:22:02.60,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,雖然達成了目的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.29,0:22:02.60,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}是真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.72,0:22:03.81,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}真的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.48,0:22:05.81,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,但完全沒有贏了她的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.92,0:22:06.02,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}可你的臉很紅哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.89,0:22:07.92,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,是你的錯覺吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.54,0:22:24.69,Takagi san—Ed-Japanese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}もっと遊んで　指を鳴らして
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.77,0:22:27.64,Takagi san—Ed-Japanese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}呼んでいる声がするわ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.03,0:22:34.27,Takagi san—Ed-Japanese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}本当も嘘も　興味がないのよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.49,0:22:37.66,Takagi san—Ed-Japanese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}指先からすり抜けてく
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.75,0:22:40.64,Takagi san—Ed-Japanese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}欲張りな笑い声も
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.00,0:22:47.36,Takagi san—Ed-Japanese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}ごちゃ混ぜにした　スープに溶かすから
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.24,0:22:54.11,Takagi san—Ed-Japanese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}音に合わせて　靴をならして
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.72,0:22:59.32,Takagi san—Ed-Japanese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}あたしだけの秘密の場所
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.58,0:23:07.34,Takagi san—Ed-Japanese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}走る雲の影を飛び越えるわ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.66,0:23:13.11,Takagi san—Ed-Japanese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}夏の匂い追いかけて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.38,0:23:19.59,Takagi san—Ed-Japanese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}あぁ夢はいつまでも覚めない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.86,0:23:25.08,Takagi san—Ed-Japanese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}歌う風のように
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.54,0:22:24.69,Takagi san—Ed-Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}再多玩玩  打個響指
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.77,0:22:27.64,Takagi san—Ed-Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}聽到了你的呼喚
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.03,0:22:34.27,Takagi san—Ed-Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}無論是真是假  我都不感興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.49,0:22:37.66,Takagi san—Ed-Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}指尖悄然滑過
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.75,0:22:40.64,Takagi san—Ed-Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}暢懷發出的笑聲
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.00,0:22:47.36,Takagi san—Ed-Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}都亂七八糟地溶進濃湯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.24,0:22:54.11,Takagi san—Ed-Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}配合著聲音  用鞋子打著節拍
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.72,0:22:59.32,Takagi san—Ed-Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}只屬於自己的秘密地方
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.58,0:23:07.34,Takagi san—Ed-Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}飛身越過那流雲的影子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.66,0:23:13.11,Takagi san—Ed-Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}追逐著夏日的芳香
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.38,0:23:19.59,Takagi san—Ed-Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}啊啊  一直在美夢中無盡徜徉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.86,0:23:25.08,Takagi san—Ed-Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}猶如謳歌的風兒一般
